{"tid":2358344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警問被捕者對攬炒十步看法","createTime":"2021-01-08T05:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T08:49:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2021938fb0c9d8a5af6bb0e7c917015db13d222d","tid":2358344,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/6HJXQSAKNVE4ZICVB7PHN4DCYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2F6HJXQSAKNVE4ZICVB7PHN4DCYA%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTITUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=0ebe866a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2F6HJXQSAKNVE4ZICVB7PHN4DCYA%2F&h=cb3be7b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/6HJXQSAKNVE4ZICVB7PHN4DCYA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警問被捕者對攬炒十步看法<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方前日以涉違反港版國安法「顛覆國家政權罪」瘋狂搜捕53人，除被捕人士中年紀最大的美籍人權律師兼民主動力司庫關尚義（John Clancey）已於昨凌晨悄悄獲釋，其他被捕人士在扣留近40小時後昨晚陸續獲釋，暫未有人被起訴。獲釋的都是初選候選人，他們對被捕莫名其妙，形容行動非常荒謬，更有被捕人士透露拘押期間反覆被警方要求「錄影會面」，警方更展示戴耀廷去年4月發表的〈真攬炒十步〉文章，問及其看法及是否參與其中，同時亦圍繞資金等問題盤問。<br />\n<br />\n據知獲釋各人暫時各准以三萬元保釋、並且被沒收旅遊證件、半年內不得離港，下月要報到。昨晚8時半起，被捕人士陸續獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員岑子杰獲釋後對被捕感到憤慨，「究竟拉我係咪好荒謬？我只係覺得由拉黎智英嗰刻已經夠荒謬！」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lQZVDAhv-vZBkbajpKkovLCU2e0=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WNGATZMXEBE63E6SVBE2PJUOAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlQZVDAhv-vZBkbajpKkovLCU2e0%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWNGATZMXEBE63E6SVBE2PJUOAI.jpg&h=36ed47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃碧雲及岑子杰昨獲准保釋後相擁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫無人被落案<br />\n<br />\n立法會前議員朱凱廸指，扣查期間曾進行五、六次錄影會面，每次都涉及不同問題。他形容如果被控，就是將「民主」二字放在法庭上審判。另有被捕人士稱，警方調查期間展示不少facebook截圖要求回應；其中有關戴耀廷去年發表、被指是今次初選顛覆「罪證」的〈真攬炒十步〉文章，截圖日子顯示是去年8月5日，認為警方「處心積慮」拘捕民主派。另有被捕人士指，警方錄口供期間多次提及「Plan B」、民研、民動及戴耀廷，包括詢問是否知道甚麼是Plan B、資金來源等，擔心「打壓網」會進一步擴大，認為需要再作評估及應對。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議員岑敖暉亦指控罪非常荒謬，「心入面覺得有啲好笑」，在警署三次錄影會面中，警方多次強調因他參與初選，而涉嫌干犯「顛覆國家政權」，他對此感到不解，不明白兩者為何被畫上等號。<br />\n<br />\n立法會前議員涂謹申直言，「。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中西區區議員梁晃維指政府打壓屬意料之內，認為今次拘捕行動證明政權是要將民主聲音趕盡殺絕。"},{"pid":"e12534dc0911f159121305907f97dd45dea1a552","tid":2358344,"uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"黑警永遠係人民公敵"},{"pid":"7e025e09e817741cca14b51eac090a143f3de4e7","tid":2358344,"uid":254383,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"屌，成班藍屍除咗褲都要著返<br />\n<br />\n顛覆咁大罪點解唔即刻告仲要有得保釋"},{"pid":"e0f42a378b84d3cdc8d2db59f64bcd9557f5569c","tid":2358344,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"唔保釋係咪會提堂，然後裁判官又會話控罪嚴重需要還柙？"},{"pid":"7697af75d1074efb149d687df37a7f800d048654","tid":2358344,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"人雖無罪，但懷賓有罪。"},{"pid":"ac38380819f78268a4127a97f5ab29bc0367f1a8","tid":2358344,"uid":173060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"做咩唔問係咪收左外國錢呢d 弱智問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6045f8ca4ae7ac3f26911530758d5e38f3a4e3","tid":2358344,"uid":38793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"a31076483747848650b33fe78bc7bc7e183dcdf8","tid":2358344,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"如果咁啱有一個拒絕保釋係咪要即時開庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc58bed77705b151add509d8c6bbb5eadea7551a","tid":2358344,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e025e09e817741cca14b51eac090a143f3de4e7","tid":2358344,"uid":254383,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"屌，成班藍屍除咗褲都要著返<br />\n<br />\n顛覆咁大罪點解唔即刻告仲要有得保釋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"其實純粹搵個藉口收晒呢班人passport<br />\n<br />\n個個月都有反對派領袖流亡 太肉酸落中共面<br />\n<br />\n中共接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要禁呢班人出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cffed5c0607518e02fa6398c5c2e55b795d335e","tid":2358344,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859b6360630eee80884e5c4ffc7f6f328ec2a6ce","tid":2358344,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"又話國安法冇得保釋嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申藍絲"},{"pid":"f3e41465054e8cff571fd46052881357bc9ab91f","tid":2358344,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a31076483747848650b33fe78bc7bc7e183dcdf8","tid":2358344,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"如果咁啱有一個拒絕保釋係咪要即時開庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"其實佢零成本<br />\n<br />\n直接用國安法踢上法庭一定還押<br />\n<br />\n反正美國嗰邊biden 已經搞掂左"},{"pid":"e174aaeeae805d16a62f8cea7e3a9e91806978fc","tid":2358344,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"問埋啲唔等洗丶唔拉更嘅問題，有咩睇法<br />\n<br />\n冇嘢講丶冇睇法，要見律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cce1a7b4589eb1e8064ab45539958989458bd2","tid":2358344,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e025e09e817741cca14b51eac090a143f3de4e7","tid":2358344,"uid":254383,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"屌，成班藍屍除咗褲都要著返<br />\n<br />\n顛覆咁大罪點解唔即刻告仲要有得保釋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"